All Packages

Package Summary 
Package Description
net.getnova.backend
This is the main package, of the nova backend.
net.getnova.backend.api.annotations
This package contains all Annotations witch are needed fo the Api System.
net.getnova.backend.api.data
This package contains all classes who are able to hold data, witch should be cached.
net.getnova.backend.api.exception
This package contains all Exceptions from the Api System.
net.getnova.backend.api.executor
This package contains all classes to execute endpoints in the Api System.
net.getnova.backend.api.handler.playground
This package contains all netty handlers witch are needed for the playground service.
net.getnova.backend.api.handler.rest
This package contains all netty handlers witch are needed for a rest api.
net.getnova.backend.api.handler.websocket
This package contains all netty handlers witch are needed for a websocket api.
net.getnova.backend.api.parser
This package contains all classes witch are needed to parse Classes witch are related to the api system.
net.getnova.backend.codec.http
This package contains all relevant stuff for the netty http codec.
net.getnova.backend.codec.http.server
This package contains all relevant stuff for the http server service/codec.
net.getnova.backend.config
This package contains all necessary stuff for the config system.
net.getnova.backend.handler
This package contains all the bootstrapping handlers for the backend.
net.getnova.backend.injection
This handle the dependency injection of the nova backend.
net.getnova.backend.json
This package contains utils to serialize and deserialize java objects.
net.getnova.backend.json.types
This package contains all special json type mappings.
net.getnova.backend.logging
This package contains logging tools for the nova backend.
net.getnova.backend.modules
Contains all stuff for the module system.
net.getnova.backend.netty
This package contains all netty relevant client and server base stuff.
net.getnova.backend.netty.codec
This package contains all netty relevant codec stuff.
net.getnova.backend.netty.server
This package contains all netty relevant server stuff.
net.getnova.backend.service
This package contains all relevant classes to manage services.
net.getnova.backend.service.event
This package contains the service event annotation and data classes.
net.getnova.backend.sql
This package contains all stuff witch is associated with a sql database connection.
net.getnova.backend.sql.model
This package contains all table model bases.
net.getnova.backend.sql.repository
This package contains all base repositories.
net.getnova.backend.tests
Some utils for thees unit tests.
